{"tid":810736,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有Uber司機涉裝車內針孔攝錄機偷拍　遭警打擊酒後駕駛時揭發 (14:46)","createTime":"2018-09-08T08:16:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T08:54:24.000Z","uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e26e42d017e2fe12c06132f8e442be3a0f975ebd","tid":810736,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:16:47.000Z","msg":"有Uber司機涉裝車內針孔攝錄機偷拍　遭警打擊酒後駕駛時揭發 (14:46)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180908/s00001/2e81d305fc0da8309e46a9f66861f367.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180908%2Fs00001%2F2e81d305fc0da8309e46a9f66861f367.jpg&h=0ef3590d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n椅背裝針孔攝錄機。(警方提供圖片)<br />\n圖4之1 - 椅背裝針孔攝錄機。(警方提供圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180908/s00001/2ebaca84e6264509a2082fd5e898be00.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180908%2Fs00001%2F2ebaca84e6264509a2082fd5e898be00.jpg&h=b4f74ab7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180908/s00001/2ebbb6ef0426f10d12f4d2337a5dbaed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180908%2Fs00001%2F2ebbb6ef0426f10d12f4d2337a5dbaed.jpg&h=592d1f3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方新界南總區交通執行及管制組特遣隊，今日凌晨在區內多處地點打擊酒後駕駛‬，共要288名司機酒精呼氣測試，其中3名年齡介乎23至66歲的本地男司機未能通過，涉嫌「酒後駕駛」被捕。<br />\n<br />\n其間，一名44歲姓黃本地男司機，在路障接受呼氣測試時不合格，帶返警署以「大機」再度測試時，錄得結果不超出法定標準。惟警員檢查其七人車時，發現有兩部針孔攝錄機，分別安裝於司機椅背及左前乘客椅背，懷疑用作偷拍後座乘客大腿一帶位置，車內2部智能電話亦發現藏有多條不雅短片。<br />\n<br />\n警方經調查後，相信黃為Uber司機，當時車上有一名女乘客。黃涉嫌「不誠實使用電腦」、「非法駕駛汽車作出租或載客取酬用途」及「駕駛汽車時沒有第三者保險」被捕，由沙田警區刑事調查隊第3隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n警方稱，會繼續加強執法，打擊酒後和藥後駕駛及其他相關違法行為，以保障市民安全，呼籲駕駛人士切勿以身試法。"},{"pid":"af015d51453dcc17911fb5cb45c7094d501943ba","tid":810736,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"在路障接受呼氣測試時不合格，帶返警署以「大機」再度測試時，錄得結果不超出法定標準。惟警員檢查其七人車時，發現有兩部針孔攝錄機<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f487f397e5140353c182800dcacac67cf5ac80d8","tid":810736,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:19:52.000Z","msg":"不孝子 抵死"},{"pid":"a3a94f4a062c19d12b54a749fcd00291a8ece7bd","tid":810736,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:21:21.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 坐監俾人屌穿屎眼啦撚樣屌你老母"},{"pid":"bbe4df1d6dec9880576ea34c174d2b6b5cc79739","tid":810736,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3a94f4a062c19d12b54a749fcd00291a8ece7bd","tid":810736,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:21:21.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 坐監俾人屌穿屎眼啦撚樣屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:43:22.000Z","msg":"不誠實&hellip;&hellip;罪可能打得甩喎"},{"pid":"3ee2288255274a958e2cb860db68c5d472c8e8a8","tid":810736,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"大陸一上車要強制全程錄音咪仲衰"},{"pid":"d38412270029f41a47c10fd620874e814736a5ee","tid":810736,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:47:30.000Z","msg":"十成九又係偷拍group d賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cdc527f141db819fe3e0e58f1bf4a292c8392d","tid":810736,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee2288255274a958e2cb860db68c5d472c8e8a8","tid":810736,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:45:05.000Z","msg":"大陸一上車要強制全程錄音咪仲衰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-08T08:52:05.000Z","msg":"可以唔出聲啫"},{"pid":"094e53ff5b675cf9e719e68c59a35f89b817ee81","tid":810736,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75cdc527f141db819fe3e0e58f1bf4a292c8392d","tid":810736,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dis